 MAC OS X
*********

Install dependencies
--------------------
Make sure the latero and latero-graphics libraries are installed. See instructions in INSTALL file for latero and latero-graphics projects.

Install X11 server:
>> sudo port install xorg-server

Build latero-demo
-----------------
>> mkdir build
>> cd build
>> cmake ..
>> make
>> ../create_app_bundle.sh

You should now be able to launch the program by clicking on the latero-demo app bundle.
